    "Figure 1a illustrate the vision transformer.The performance of ViT is superior to CNNs while using fewer resources.",
    "However, due to its weaker inductive bias, it needs more data augmentation or regularization while training on smaller datasets.",
    "ViT represents image inputs as a sequence of image patches and requires a significant amount of data to achieve optimal performance.",
    "The mathematical formulation of kernel convolution in CNN can be described by Eq. 1.where the f represent the input image and h denotes the kernel.",
    "The indices of columns and rows of the result matrix are marked with n and m, respectively."
